{"tid":1157381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逃犯條例】東方引消息：政府最快明預告ㅤ直接呈立法會大會審議","createTime":"2019-05-16T08:47:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-16T18:09:32.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"03a6a5ce25a66a32268cef6be584bc06d6a73a97","tid":1157381,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T08:47:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/43190528961_b7d86a6631_o_52LEn20copy_AZjnA_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F43190528961_b7d86a6631_o_52LEn20copy_AZjnA_1200x0.png&h=84505499&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n立法會民主派與建制派今日早上舉行協商會議，討論修訂逃犯條例法案委員會的困局，但雙方不歡而散，《東方日報》今日引述消息，政府最快於明天立法會預告，把逃犯條例修訂草案，直接遞交上立法會大會審議。<br />\n<br />\n信報政情專欄余錦賢今日亦指出，建制議員早已認為今早會談僅屬行禮如儀，事實「西環」已關達指令，法案鐵定「直上大會」。<br />\n<br />\n立法會前主席曾鈺成在周日出席電視節目最先提出，若法案委員會繼續無法順利運作，可繞過法委會直接將逃犯條例修訂草案，提交大會恢復二讀，「有何不好？現在完全失效，法案委員會開不到會。凡有爭議性的法案，在法案委員會商討了，去到大會由頭講一次，好像沒開過法案委員會一樣。」<br />\n<br />\n不過，部分建制派及民主派亦曾反對建議，實政圓桌立法會議員田北辰更指，此例一開如廢法案委員會，必定後患無窮。公民黨楊岳橋強調法案委員會有其作用，議員可以逐條條文審議，官員亦必須立即回應議員提問，但在大會就不同，議員發言後，才由官員在最後一併回應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/逃犯條例-東方引消息-政府最快明預告%E1%85%A0直接呈立法會大會審議/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E6%9D%B1%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%95%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%9C%80%E5%BF%AB%E6%98%8E%E9%A0%90%E5%91%8A%25E1%2585%25A0%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E5%91%88%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E5%A4%A7%E6%9C%83%E5%AF%A9%E8%AD%B0%2F&d=nKoZ4xrs0zkQ%2F022jTHdfyIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=50df0dcc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E6%9D%B1%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%95%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%9C%80%E5%BF%AB%E6%98%8E%E9%A0%90%E5%91%8A%25E1%2585%25A0%E7%9B%B4%E6%8E%A5%E5%91%88%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E5%A4%A7%E6%9C%83%E5%AF%A9%E8%AD%B0%2F&h=9aeb60f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/逃犯條例-東方引消息-政府最快明預告%E1%85%A0直接呈立法會大會審議/</a>"},{"pid":"1134d00eff4f20dc7f6fef6ec0f79e0e7d9a927e","tid":1157381,"uid":2757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T08:49:41.000Z","msg":"你以為死咗就唔駛引導翻嚟鞭屍呀？"},{"pid":"8816c6038f2739417c93576b04a9dd1e1f1e6aa2","tid":1157381,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T08:51:12.000Z","msg":"補血劍等唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"483b5a37a60a7692e878b514676ea127e96d5166","tid":1157381,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"1134d00eff4f20dc7f6fef6ec0f79e0e7d9a927e","tid":1157381,"uid":2757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T08:49:41.000Z","msg":"你以為死咗就唔駛引導翻嚟鞭屍呀？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T08:55:28.000Z","msg":"凍結同充公資產<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89c9b744d22f2d15be051e4313ffa5178fd560a2","tid":1157381,"uid":10157,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T09:10:29.000Z","msg":"商家佬抵死，之前跟隊DQ得咁開心<br />\n最大贏家真係有曬步驟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e7f852ded09757b26317889b2793ccd1c88e3d5","tid":1157381,"uid":242301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T09:33:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e29c88c012566fa48519fed14c237997750efd31","tid":1157381,"uid":216664,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T09:40:33.000Z","msg":"準備行動"},{"pid":"b210caddc0135b8c24e983c4cbdc53b1fd5cd34e","tid":1157381,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T11:34:52.000Z","msg":"星期五提上立法會，市民星期六日咪會有機會俾反應？政府未必會聽日，最有可能係下星期一，全世界仲有四日工要返"},{"pid":"ad26b498631a13f9c948638039a92405daa0ebeb","tid":1157381,"uid":242301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T16:23:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"987d817503d304d3c413